name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: WELO - THE NEW WAY TO WORK

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Welo is about bringing people together into an online work environment.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension integrates Google Meet with Welo to provide a seamless and enhanced virtual meeting experience. It helps optimize network requests and ensures a smoother workflow by managing content from both Welo and Google Meet without accessing user data. In addition show your idle state on your user avatar. This way your teams know if you're away from keyboard.
